OL,3,CFreedom of Dudley Borough Award
OL,4,Capproved for Jude Bellingham and
OL,5,CMorgan Rogers
OL,7,FDudley Council has approved plans to
OL,8,Fbestow the borough's highest civic
OL,9,Fhonour on football heroes Jude
OL,10,FBellingham and Morgan Rogers.
OL,12,FThe two players, who are currently
OL,13,Frepresenting England at the World Cup,
OL,14,Fwere both born in the borough, and
OL,15,Fhave been added to its Freedom of the
OL,16,FBorough honours list.
OL,18,FCouncil members also approved plans to
OL,19,Foffer Freedom to Councillor Shaukat
OL,20,FAli, and former Dudley College CEO
OL,21,FLowell Williams.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
