OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784099888
OL,3,CFreedom of Dudley Borough Award
OL,4,Capproved for Jude Bellingham and
OL,5,CMorgan Rogers
OL,7,F"From our Armed Forces veterans, who
OL,8,Fhave shown extraordinary courage and
OL,9,Fsacrifice in service to our country,
OL,10,Fto community champions, sporting role
OL,11,Fmodels and dedicated public servants,
OL,12,Feach has made a lasting impact and
OL,13,Fbrought great pride to our borough.
OL,15,F"Whether through serving their
OL,16,Fcountry, inspiring the next
OL,17,Fgeneration, supporting their
OL,18,Fcommunities or dedicating decades to
OL,19,Fpublic service, these individuals and
OL,20,Forganisations have helped shape
OL,21,FDudley's story.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,347,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784099888
OL,3,CFreedom of Dudley Borough Award
OL,4,Capproved for Jude Bellingham and
OL,5,CMorgan Rogers
OL,7,F"It is only right that we recognise
OL,8,Ftheir achievements and celebrate the
OL,9,Fdifference they have made to the lives
OL,10,Fof others.
OL,12,F"On behalf of the council and the
OL,13,Fpeople of Dudley borough, I offer my
OL,14,Fheartfelt congratulations to all those
OL,15,Fbeing honoured."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
