PN,34605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F346A1784099888
OL,3,CFreedom of Dudley Borough Award
OL,4,Capproved for Jude Bellingham and
OL,5,CMorgan Rogers
OL,7,FFreedom of the Borough has previously
OL,8,Fbeen granted to notable figures
OL,9,Fincluding Sir Lenny Henry, Jordanne
OL,10,FWhiley, B (SWWY) Squadron, The Royal
OL,11,FYeomanry and, more recently, Royal
OL,12,FNavy veteran, the late Joe Bullock in
OL,13,Frecognition of his wartime service.
OL,15,FFormal presentations of the Freedom of
OL,16,Fthe Borough and Honorary Alderman
OL,17,Fawards will take place at a civic
OL,18,Fceremony later this year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/5
